Yep you speaketh the truth <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /> Here's the Sokl oow charm summary.
<br />

<br />
All non oow mobs over 64 are flagged uncharmable.
<br />

<br />
Non oow charm works on oow mobs, it is the mob that hits less under charm, it isn't the charm that reduces the damage. This was achieved by having two damage tables. They can apply this principle to any mob, oow or not but currently only oow mobs are affected.
<br />

<br />
Charm dps in oow seems to be capped at around 100dps which is pretty close to what you can do with an animation and nukes, except shiny bob won't tear you a new one every 5 minutes.
<br />

<br />
The best use for charm at the moment is reverse charm where you use a rooted hasted ex pet to beat your pet down to a few percent then break charm and nuke for full xp. 
<br />
I've used it once to prevent a wipe when we got trained in wos, but generally it's useless for cc.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
