It's ok, that charmed pets hit a bit lesser than normal. It's ok because i think it's wrong that a pet can outdamage a whole group.
<br />
But i think also, that the reduction in damage implemented in OoW zones is way too much...
<br />
Especially when considering the risks when charm is breaking...</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 24px; line-height: normal"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: orange"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=588112" target="_blank" class="postlink">Silamael Darkomen</a></span></span></span>
